            <description><![CDATA[<h1>MacTC 1.0 (347)</h1>
<ul>
  <li>Pinned-live trend rendering is smoother and stays cheaper during live updates, which keeps the chart steadier while it remains at 60 Hz.</li>
  <li>Sparkle auto-update support is now part of the release path, so future beta updates can ship through the public GitHub Pages surface.</li>
  <li>No helper reinstall is required for this update.</li>
</ul>
